I found this collection at Walmart and I love spy movies so I went for it and all 4 movies are great. State of Play and Spy Game are both big Hollywood movies and were excellent spy/conspiracy movies though they I felt both of them looked at the time and thought it was time to wrap it up and the ending of both movies were not as good as the rest of the movie. Breach had an incredible performance by the lead actor and Closed Circuit was the best consistently good spy movie. When I think of buying a movie I think as to whether I would watch it again and I will watch all four movies every once in a while.

There is a problem with the dvd's.  When you stop them, it is extremely difficult to get them to play again.  I had to eject them and reinsert the dvd and then press play in order to get the dvd to play.  I have tried these dvd's in multiple dvd players (sony, panasonic, a PS4, xbox 360, toshiba) and the results are the same.  The movies themselves are good films, but the problem makes me think I should have ordered them individually from another production company.  What a waste of money.
